ios.subtitle: Make a routine & put on a show

editorialNotes.standard: Bursting with beats and energy, Toca Dance will make the whole family want to get up and groove. This incredibly cute game puts kids in charge of their own musical productionchoosing dancers, costumes and techno tracks, and choreographing moves using simple swipes and taps. Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoffan awesome video you can sharewill encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.

editorialNotes.tagline: Create and rule your own universe
editorialNotes.standard: We love learning about the celestial bodies in our own galaxy, but weve always dreamed of building our own. SPACE gives us the power to create stunningly detailed stars and planets, forging a virtual universe that follows the laws of astrophysics. Its a heady thrill to be the master of our own miniature heavenswhipping up red dwarfs, gas giants, and comets that blaze through the cosmos at the tap of a finger.
